{"tid":216781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾百佳抄惠康","createTime":"2017-04-25T12:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T12:32:52.000Z","uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5db40dc3886df8c85246a7398c87f8d3105e7ba2","tid":216781,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾百佳抄惠康<br />\n由貨架擺設收銀儲積分賣肉賣壽司就連個名嘅格式都抄埋做xx超級市場咁，都仲咁多人去買野支持，成班港豬冇得救。<br />\n<br />\n仲有d便利店，抄到一樣咁濟，除左個名<br />\n<br />\n茶記又係互相抄，快餐中餐西餐連名都抄<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩萬寧屈臣又係抄，d雜貨鋪又係互抄，化妝品店又係互抄<br />\n<br />\n成個香港成個地球人都係不停抄，人類冇撚得救。<br />\n<br />\n都係返去宇宙唯一原創嘅高登算數。"},{"pid":"502557d3c1a7ec25a53e74fa85b2f3590a3a8650","tid":216781,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"百佳同惠康係同一個老闆"},{"pid":"d11458cfa71dbaa7d0b68197940135d9f2013df5","tid":216781,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬做咩抄我呼吸"},{"pid":"65176f84339aa1bac8366f01fc29b68adf44433b","tid":216781,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"精神病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703d9dea0f329c81d2d05fc02d567092f6059dc5","tid":216781,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"on9 樓主抄我啲中文字"},{"pid":"e4ae8b37c326d452a9ce7c5202c9ae19ff0ef186","tid":216781,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百佳同惠康係同一個老闆</blockquote><br />\n百佳李嘉誠，惠康係怡和架喎"},{"pid":"02ea8dd8e2bdee84e298dda27976503a96a44c4a","tid":216781,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"抽得好柒"},{"pid":"72e8a76294c8867d66f1e6615c62afbd4a7b6031","tid":216781,"uid":98381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百佳同惠康係同一個老闆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor